.TH "GAMEPAD.INDEX" "3JS" "December 27, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
Gamepad.index \- Gamepad: index property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]Gamepad.index\f[B]\f[R] property of the
\f[CR]Gamepad\f[R] interface returns an integer that is
auto\-incremented to be unique for each device currently connected to
the system.
.PP
This can be used to distinguish multiple controllers; a gamepad that is
disconnected and reconnected will retain the same index.
.SH VALUE
A \f[CR]number\f[R].
.SH EXAMPLES
.IP
.EX
window.addEventListener(\(dqgamepadconnected\(dq, () \f[B]=>\f[R] {
  \f[B]const\f[R] gp = navigator.getGamepads()[0];
  gamepadInfo.textContent = \(gaGamepad connected at index ${gp.index}: ${gp.id}.\(ga;
});
.EE
.SH SEE ALSO
Using the Gamepad API
